## 🚀 Short Product Summary

A **Python-based No-Code Desktop UI Automation Tool** that enables **non-technical users** to record, build, and execute workflows using **visual object detection instead of fragile coordinates**.

---

## ⭐ Key Highlights (vs Market Tools like UiPath)

* **🧠 Hybrid Execution Engine**
  Uses *object recognition (OpenCV)* + *fallback coordinates* → far more reliable than basic macro tools

* **🎯 Visual Object-Based Automation**
  Capture UI elements once → reuse across workflows (like real RPA)

* **🔁 Smart Click Engine**
  Auto-retry + timeout + fallback → reduces failure rate significantly

* **🧩 Beginner-Friendly Design**
  Clean UI, dropdowns, no coding required

* **⚙️ Modular Architecture**
  Recorder, Player, Vision, Workflow → easy to extend & maintain

* **🖼️ Region-Based Image Detection**
  Faster + more accurate object finding (optimized vs naive full-screen scan)

* **🧪 Debuggable System**
  Object validation, wait conditions, execution status

---

## ⚡ Core Features (Crisp)

* Record mouse & keyboard actions
* Capture UI elements via snipping tool
* Build workflows with step editor
* Execute with:

  * Click Object
  * Wait for Object
  * Validate Object
* Playback speed + stop hotkey
* Object repository (JSON-based)
* Smart retry & failure handling
* Workflow step management (reorder, duplicate, delete)

